{"about_the_game":"<i>Igor</i> must <strong>escape from a mental asylum</strong>, but it\u2019s not going to be easy. There are two (2) rather obvious reasons:<br><br>1. <i>Igor</i> is constrained by <strong>a straitjacket</strong>.<br>2. The asylum\u2019s corridors are filled with <strong>tranquilizers-ready guards</strong> (and other obstacles).<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/654430/extras/shotgun_03.jpg?t=1655225642\" /><br><br>In addition to the dangers haunting outside, <i>Igor</i> is going through <strong>a war inside his head</strong>: his <strong>psychotic imaginary friend</strong>, <i>Flead</i>, is constantly demanding him to cancel his stupid escaping attempt.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/654430/extras/Flead_Gif_3.jpg?t=1655225642\" /><br><br>The INSANE story takes place in <strong>a mysterious mental asylum</strong> which is known from its <strong>dark-ish history</strong> of utilizing questionable alternative treatments. The only thing even more mysterious, is <strong>the genius mastermind</strong>, <i>Head Doctor</i>, who is running the place...<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/654430/extras/Head_Doctor_with_PONU.png?t=1655225642\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">FEATURES</h2><br><strong>Three (3) multi-level game worlds</strong>, each of them packed with unique gameplay features<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><i>Special Patients</i> has <strong>kittens</strong>.<br></li><li><i>Ancient Section</i> has <strong>abandoned motorized machines</strong> and <strong>dynamite</strong>.<br></li><li><i>Top Secret Area</i> has <strong>teleports</strong> and other cool hi-tech devices from the future.<br></li><li>... and <strong>much more</strong>!</li></ul><br>All asylum\u2019s <strong>secrets shall be... unveiled!</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Collect</strong> <i>Random Notes</i> that our scatterbrained <i>Head Doctor</i> has left behind! <br></li><li><strong>Discover</strong> <i>Fine Pieces of Art</i>!<br></li><li><strong>Hoard</strong> <i>Funny Hats</i>!<br></li><li><strong>Reveal</strong> the ultimate truth, <i>The Understanding to Everything</i>!</li></ul><br><strong>Greatly praised OST</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>The soundtrack was nominated as &quot;<strong>Best Game Music</strong>&quot; at Game Audio Awards 2018.<br></li><li><strong>11 pieces of music</strong> composed &amp; arranged by maestros, <i>Toni Aaltola</i> and <i>Tommi Ilonen</i>.</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"STATUS: SPECIAL PATIENT","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/654430/7e64e8c4c1d2aa7a74d708855394c7026e38eb96.jpg"},{"name":"STATUS: HISTORY GRADUATE","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/654430/29d3dde6992b79e7f4f7a039e3c1365e9005ad65.jpg"},{"name":"STATUS: IN THE YEAR 3000","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/654430/d0906aec9f76de6f7ebe77f8150092704bc666f7.jpg"},{"name":"STATUS: MASOCHIST","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/654430/692cf6d193ebcc54a5196f47c84494fb23308a78.jpg"},{"name":"STATUS: STALKER ","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/654430/d4b7b69d0372994204c4bf5c36040fe7e3770e1e.jpg"},{"name":"STATUS: UNKNOWN","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/654430/5dc8dbc9958c272229ced02a6092e7bd0b994b3d.jpg"},{"name":"STATUS: HIPSTER","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/654430/33a4375b35adfe544f85961448ecaa0c902818e1.jpg"},{"name":"STATUS: ANTI-HIPSTER","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/654430/9f609d3a57b8ae412ec4fbcdff1ecac0fa7e54ba.jpg"},{"name":"STATUS: FUNNY HAT HOARDER","path"